&lt;h4 id="fine-grained-access-control">Fine-Grained Access Control&lt;/h4>
&lt;p>Limit who can &lt;strong>read&lt;/strong>, &lt;strong>write&lt;/strong>, or &lt;strong>delete&lt;/strong> specific resources within a namespace.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>